WEBVTT

00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:03.800
Hello, my name's Steve,
and I'm the Clinical Lead and Head

00:00:03.880 --> 00:00:07.240
of Department for Psychological Services
here at the Hospice.

00:00:07.320 --> 00:00:09.320
We are a group of talking therapists,

00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:14.720
and we work with the patient,
family members, pre and post bereavement.

00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:16.760
We have these beautiful counselling rooms

00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:19.720
here on site,
but we can also work with you in your

00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:23.800
home, and we can also do
online and telephone sessions.

00:00:23.880 --> 00:00:27.240
We're here to provide that emotional

00:00:27.320 --> 00:00:32.160
support and stability when you feel the
time is right for you to engage with us.

00:00:32.240 --> 00:00:33.680
We leave it with you.

00:00:33.680 --> 00:00:35.800
You can speak with our
colleagues on the IPU.

00:00:35.880 --> 00:00:37.400
You can call in yourself.

00:00:37.480 --> 00:00:40.800
You can also access us
via the community team.

00:00:40.880 --> 00:00:42.920
But please reach out.
We're always here.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:46.880
Services are available throughout
the week and also in the evenings.

00:00:46.960 --> 00:00:48.000
Now it's time to move on.

